snippet.title: improvised COVID songs and amateur covers featuring The Green-Willow Sound (my cousin)
snippet.description:
Are they going to lock us up forever? Will the vaccine save us? We make up songs about coronavirus as the lockdown continues in Canada. We didn't know all the words to the covers, we messed up the chords, so we improvised. Hope you enjoy this her habits vlog featuring my cousin The Green-Willow Sound (you can subscribe to his channel below)

subscribe to The Green-Willow Sound here👇herehttps://www.youtube.com/channel/UCThbWxejDXRASY96qRrCUWg?sub_confirmation=1
📸Instagram: @lonewolf8835👉https://www.instagram.com/lonewolf8835/

check out my original song "alone in this world"👉https://youtu.be/1-Kw3Eh7r74
follow me on 📸Instagram: @herhabitschannel👉https://www.instagram.com/herhabitschannel/
